Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.69,0:22:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\fn@黑体\frz-90\b0\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(280,277)}那樣不是很酷嗎\N
